title: Wonder Momo
synopsis: One day, a group of aliens planning to take over the Earth invade Tokyo. Momoko, who aspires to be an idol, gets involved in the ensuing fight, albeit in an unexpected manner. Warudemon, king of the alien empire, uses various tactics to hunt down Momoko and the people around her. Momoko decides to stand up against this aggression.
voices: ['Fujiwara, Yuka', 'Komatsu, Misaki', 'Momoi, Haruko', 'Imaruoka, Atsushi', 'Inami, Anju', 'Tamaru, Atsushi']
